keyFacts: An Instagram account with the username 'Ghislainemaxwell' was created on August 14, 2019, from IP address 104.219.99.170.
The business record was generated on July 23, 2020, in response to a legal request, specifically to check for NCMEC cybertip reports linked to the account.
No NCMEC cybertip reports, registered email addresses, or login records were found associated with the account for the searched period (March 15, 2020, to June 15, 2020).
The account was still active at the time the records were generated in mid-2020.
The document is part of a forensic data extraction, indicating law enforcement interest in Ghislaine Maxwell's online activity.
